erience research focuses on how an audience\u2019s exposure and understanding are impacted by the difference mediums used for [pain]byte. <\/b><\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Abstract: for EVA- London 2017 Our\u00a0initial stage paper focuses on the Virtual Reality (VR) experience of the [pain]Byte ballet. The live and VR experience debut October 1st 2017, as part of the Brighton digital festival. Specifically, the development of the&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[64,46,42,101],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1488"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1488"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1488\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1489,"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1488\/revisions\/1489"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1488"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1488"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1488"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}